  <constraints>
    <constraint source="ADR-012">Shared components — Fluent UI v9; do NOT introduce v8 or custom CSS color values.</constraint>
    <constraint source="ADR-021">Fluent v9 dark-mode compliance — all colors via semantic tokens; dark-mode UI test mandatory.</constraint>
