    <criterion testable="true">Object-typed fields (`{ type: "object", properties: {...} }`) render as Fluent v9 labeled key-value blocks; each nested property has a `Label` + value.</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">Nested array properties within an object REUSE task 040's bulleted list rendering (no duplicate implementation).</criterion>
