    <criterion testable="true">Depth guard implemented: nested object-of-object (depth ≥ 2) falls back to compact JSON.stringify with a TODO marker; widget does NOT recurse infinitely or crash.</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">Backward compatibility preserved (actions without outputSchema render as today).</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">ADR-021 dark-mode compliance: zero hard-coded colors; all colors use Fluent UI v9 semantic tokens.</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">ADR-030 PaneEventBus: no new channels; widget consumes existing `workspace.*` channels only.</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">Unit tests cover: object dispatch happy path; nested array within object; depth-≥-2 fallback; task-040 array case regression. All pass.</criterion>
